RECEPTION Section::::Reception .
On review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes , the season holds an approval rating of 100 % based on 10 reviews , with an average rating of 6.78 .
The site 's critical consensus reads , " After seven years of friendship , New Girl signs off with a thoughtful , funny final season that bids a proper adieu to its colourful cast of characters . "
